#TBT to May 15, 2020.

125 days ago House passed #HeroesAct to extend $600 emergency unemployment, provide 2nd stimulus checks, food &amp; rental assistance, and protect health &amp; safety of students, teachers, and families.

@SenateGOP &amp; @WhiteHouse since... https://t.co/8qcdEhnWwO

SHOCKING: recent survey of Black &amp; Latinx women biz owners found 70% reported #COVID19 caused decrease/loss of revenue &amp; 90% are unable to pay themselves a sustainable income. 

Women-owned biz cannot be left--this must be fixed!

@FSCDems Diversity &amp; Inclusion hearing.
